        "content": "<p>There's <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Topology/Homeomorph/Lemmas.html#Continuous.homeoOfEquivCompactToT2\">Continuous.homeoOfEquivCompactToT2</a> etc.</p>",
